title: Songs That Remind You Of An Ex + Dan & Shay Stop By
itunes:title: Songs That Remind You Of An Ex + Dan & Shay Stop By
description:
Bobby, Amy, Lunchbox and Eddie share stories of songs that remind them of their exes. Also, Dan and Shay stop by to perform a parody of their hit song "Tequila" called "Chipotle."
